quran[564]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Okhururalana khushina shiabarebananga
  78,2,Okhurulana nende amacheni amakhongo
  78,3,Kalia akabawukhanangamwo
  78,4,"Tawe lekha butswa, ahambi hano baletsa okhumanya"
  78,5,"Mana Khandi tawe lekha butswa, ahambi hano baletsa okhumanya"
  78,6,Shikhwakhola liloba okhuba shinga obulili
  78,7,Ne tsingulu okhuba tsisiilo
  78,8,Ne ni khubaloonga tsimbia tsibili (eshisatsa neshikhasi)
  78,9,Ne nikhukhola okhukona khwenyu okhuba okhuwuluukha
  78,10,Ne nikhukhola eshilo okhuba eshifwalo
  78,11,"Ne\tnikhukhola\teshitere\tokhuba shiokhukhalabanila obulamu"
  78,12,Ne nikhumbakha hekulu wenyu amakulu saba aka amani
  78,13,Ne nikhukasia itaa yobulafu nende obubafu
  78,14,Ne nikhwishia amatsi karulanga bwangu okhurula mumaleesi
  78,15,kachila khurusie khuko imele nende emimela
  78,16,Nende emikunda chiemisala chiatilana
  78,17,Toto inyanga yobwaukhasi yarebwaho khubise
  78,18,"Inyanga yolwika lulikhupwa, nanyu muliitsa mumikanda"
  78,19,Ne likulu liliikulwa liaba shinga emiliango
  78,20,Ne tsingulu tsilisiulwa tsiaba shinga amaweruweru
  78,21,Toto Jahanamu iliindanga
  78,22,Niyo eshimenyo shia Abakhayi
  78,23,Balimenyamwo tsinyanga netsinyanga
  78,24,Shibalipilamwo shiosi shiosi eshinyifu nohomba eshinywebwa tawe
  78,25,Halali amatsi kayile nende amafila
  78,26,Nomurungo kubayela
  78,27,Toto bo Shibasubilanga mbu khuliba nende inyanga yemikabo tawe
  78,28,Ne nibayingana muno khubimanyisio biefu
  78,29,"Nebuli\teshindu\tkhwatililila mubuhandiche"
  78,30,Kho mupile! Shikhubameta shiosi shiosi tawe halali eshinyasio
  78,31,toto abaria Nyasaye nibo balihonokokha
  78,32,(balinyoola) emekunda nende tsizabibu
  78,33,Nende abakhana bayelana ninabo
  78,34,Nende tsigilasi tsitsule (ebinywebwa ebilayi)
  78,35,Shibaliwulilamwo obusilu nohomba amayinji tawe
  78,36,Omurungo ukhurula Khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi Omurungo kuyela
  78,37,Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo nende biosi bilimwo Omunji wetsimbabaasi shibalilomaloma imbeli wuwe tawe
  78,38,"Inyanga ya Roho (Jibreel) alisinjila nende Abamalaika khulunyaali. Shalilomaloma yesiyesi tawe okhuyiniakhwo ulia ulifuchililwa nende Nyasaye wetsimbabaasi, ne aliboola obulaamba bwonyene"
  78,39,Eyo niyo inyanga yatoto. Ne owenya atile injila akalushile Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi
  78,40,"Toto efwe khubekanyisilia eshinyasio shili ahambi okhuula. Inyanga ya Omundu alilola kayakhola omwene. Ne Omukhayi aliboola mbu: “manyanga ndakhabeele liloba!”"
  79,1,Nditsuba Khubamalaika bakhunyulanga (emioyo cha bakhayi) nende amaani
  79,2,Nende balia barusinjia (emioyo chiabasuubili) kaala
  79,3,Nende balia bakulukhanga mwikulu bukulukha
  79,4,Nende balia bashilananga tsimbilo (nende emioyo chiabasuubili okhuyila mwikulu)
  79,5,"Nende balia bakaasinjia amakhuwa. (emioyo emibii nichinyoola eshinyasio, ne emilayi nichisangaasibwa)"
  79,6,Inyanga yolwika lulikhupwa lweyimbeli (lulirenjia buli eshindu)
  79,7,Ne ulwika lundi lulilondakhwo
  79,8,Inyanga eyo emioyo chilirengarenga khuburi
  79,9,Tsimoni tsiachio tsilikhookha. (tsilihenga hasi)
  79,10,"(Abakhayi) baboolanga mbu: “khulikalusibwa toto shinga khwali?” (Khulilamusibwa)"
  79,11,Olwakhuliba ebikumba bibulungukha
  79,12,"Baboola mbu: “okhukalusibwa okho nikhweshikhaya (khwifwe! )”"
  79,13,Kho toto okhulamusibwa okho ni oluyoka lulala lwonyene
  79,14,hawo na hawo buli eshiloonje shiliba mushikuri eshiya
  79,15,Koo! lwakhuulilakhwo Olukano lwa Musa
  79,16,Olwa Nyasaye wuwe yamulanga mulitwoma lio luyali lia T’uwaa
  79,17,"Tsia ewa Firauni, toto ye yaburirira"
  79,18,"Umuboolele mbu: “Koo ochama okhuba Omutswenufu?”"
  79,19,Ekhwimilile khu Nyasaye wo onyoole okhumuria
  79,20,Mana namwenchesia ebimanyisio ebikhongo
  79,21,Ne naloba nakhaila elala
  79,22,"Khandi nakalukha inyuma, nakhola eshinani. (Okhukania Abandu balafuchilila Musa tawe)"
  79,23,Nakhung’asia Abandu nalaanga
  79,24,"Naboola mbu: “nesie Nyasaye wenyu Omukhongo.”"
  79,25,Kho Omulonji namutila namuhelesia eshinyasio khukayaboola kokhumalilikha (nesie Nyasaye wenyue omukhongo) nende kayaranjilila (Abulaho Nyasaye wundi owulali esie)
  79,26,toto esho neshimanyisio khubalia baria Nyasaye
  79,27,Koo! Nobutinyu okhuloonga enywe nohomba likulu? Ye niye waliumbakha
  79,28,"yalichingula, nalikasia obulayi"
  79,29,"Ne nara eshilima mushilo shiayio, ne nayiniamwo eshitere"
  79,30,Akhurula awo nakwalasia liloba
  79,31,Narusiamwo amatsikayio nende emimela
  79,32,Ne nabuusia tsingulu
  79,33,Khubukhala bwenyu nende ibiayo bienyu
  79,34,Olwamatinyu amakhongo kaliula
  79,35,Inyanga yomundu aliitsulila kayakhola
  79,36,ne jahanamu ilisitibwa khu ulola
  79,37,ne ulia waburirira mubufuru
  79,38,mana nachama muno ubulamu bweshialo
  79,39,toto jahanamu neshimenyo shishie
  79,40,"Ne ulia waria okhwema imbeli Wa Nyasaye wuwe , nakaania omwoyo kukwe obwikombi"
  79,41,Toto oyo Mwikulu nishiliba eshimenyo shishie
  79,42,Bakhurebanga ebise bieyindukho biliba lina
  79,43,Oli nashina ewe wakhanyala okhuyirumbula
  79,44,Obumalilishi bweyinyanga eyo buli khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi
  79,45,Toto ewe oli butswa Omwikanyilisi khu ulia owaria inyanga eyo
  79,46,"Olwa baliyilola inyanga eyo, balikaala mbu shibamenya khwo (khushialo) tawe halali ingolobe ndala nohomba eshitere shiayo"
  80,1,Yakhulusia obweni namukhupila likosi
  80,2,Khulwokhwitsilwa nende Omuwofu
  80,3,Ne nishina shikhumanyia ye awundi anyala ukhwitwenula
  80,4,Nohomba aletsulisibwa mana ametsulisio kamukhoonye
  80,5,"Ne\tulia wilola mbu kamubulilamwo oluchendo"
  80,6,Nawe niye oworeerekhwo eshinani
  80,7,"Shikali\tkhwiwe\ttawe\tnakhaya okhutswenukha"
  80,8,Ne ulia ukhwitsila neshinani
  80,9,Naye naririre
  80,10,Niye niwokhupila likosi
  80,11,"shikali\tkario\ttawe!\tkhuno nokhwitsulisania"
  80,12,Ulia uchama yetsulile
  80,13,Kali mutsimbapulo tsiahebwa oluyali
  80,14,Tsiarebwa hekulu tsinzwenufu
  80,15,Tsili mumikhono chia Abamalaika Abahandichi
  80,16,Boluyali abalayi
  80,17,"Omundu\tyasikha!\tNishina shimukholanga aba omukhayi"
  80,18,Yalongwa okhurula khushina
  80,19,"okhurulana nende indonyande ya amaatsi kolwibulo, yamuloonga mana namubalilila"
  80,20,Mana namwanguyilisilia injila
  80,21,Mana namufwisia namura mushilindwa
  80,22,Mana nalichama alimulamusia
  80,23,Tawe! Ashili akhumala kayamulomesia
  80,24,Kho Omundu ahenjekhwo eshilibwa shishie
  80,25,Toto efwe khwayomboola amatsi buyomboola
  80,26,Ne nikhukalukhasia liloba bukalukhasia
  80,27,Ne nikhumesiamwo imele
  80,28,Nende tsizabibu nende eliani liamasafu
  80,29,Nende emizaituna nende mitende
  80,30,"Nende\temikunda\tchiemisala chiasitanakhwo obulayi"
  80,31,"Nende\tebiamo,\tnende\tolwayilo lwemiruko"
  80,32,Khulwo obukhala bwenyu nende ebiruche bienyu
  80,33,Mana shingala omwayukho kuliitsa
  80,34,Inyanga yo Omundu alimwilukha Omusiani wabu
  80,35,Nende Nyinamwana nende Samwana
  80,36,"Nende\tOmukhaye\twuwe\tnende Abanabe"
  80,37,Buli shiamulala aliba nende akeke kamuyela
  80,38,"Inyanga\teyo\tobweni\tbundi buling’enang’ena"
  80,39,Bulitsekha nibusangalile
  80,40,Ne obweni bundi inyanga eyo buliba nende olufu
  80,41,Ishilima tititi shilibufunikha
  80,42,Abo nibo Abakhayi abakholi betsimbi
  81,1,Olwe Eliuba lilifumbwafubwa
  81,2,Ne Olwe tsing’ining’ini tsilikwa
  81,3,Ne olwe tsingulu tsilirusibwaho
  81,4,Ne olwe tsingamia tsili inda tsililekhwa
  81,5,"Ne\tolwe\ttsisolo\ttsiomwiswa tsilikhung’asibwa"
  81,6,Ne olwe Tsinyanza tsiliakha omulilo
  81,7,Ne olwe emioyo chilibukananibwa
  81,8,Ne omukhana wayabilwa omulamu Olwa alireebwa
  81,9,Khumbii shina yayererwa
  81,10,Ne olwe ebitabu bilisaalasibwa
  81,11,Ne olwe likulu lilirusibwaho
  81,12,Ne olwa Jahannamu ilisitibwa omulilo
  81,13,Ne olwa mwikulu ilisitibwa ahambi
  81,14,Buli Omundu alimanya shiayakhola
  81,15,"Nditsuba\tkhutsing’ining’ini lwatsikalukhanga inyuma"
  81,16,"Tsitsitsanga, mana khandi tsifisa"
  81,17,Ne olweshilo shitsitsanga nishichelela
  81,18,Ne eshialo nishitsia okhushia
  81,19,toto Kano ni amakhuwa komurumwa woluyali
  81,20,"Owamaani, Oweshisaala shioluyali ewa Nyasaye"
  81,21,Uwulilungwa mana khandi Omurechelefu
  81,22,Ne owashienywe uno Shali Omulalu tawe
  81,23,Ne toto bwene yamulola (jibreel) netsimoni tsie mubulafu
  81,24,Naye Shali Omwimani khumakhuwa kefisa tawe
  81,25,Nohomba kano shikali amakhuwa ka Shetani washienwa tawe
  81,26,Ne mutsitsanga yena
  81,27,Ne Ikurani ino ni eshitsulisio butswa khubiloonje biosi
  81,28,Khu yesiyesi mwinywe wenyanga okhulunjikha
  81,29,Ne enywe shimulenya tawe halali okhuula yeenye Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje biosi
  82,1,Olwe likulu lilisambukha
  82,2,Ne olwe tsing’ining’ini tsilibulungukha
  82,3,Ne olwe tsinyanza tsiliarulwa
  82,4,Ne olwebilindwa biliyabululwa
  82,5,Buli Omundu alimanya shayakhola imbeli nende mukhumalilikha
  82,6,Ewe Omundu! Ni shina shiakhukatia khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi Woluyali
  82,7,"Ulia\twakhuloonga,\tobulayi nakhuleng’ania"
  82,8,"Nakhukasia\tmulikondo\tliomwene yachama"
  82,9,Shikali kario tawe! halali enywe muyingananga mbu inyanga yomurungo shilibaho tawe
  82,10,Ne obwatoto muli nende Abalindi
  82,11,Abahandichi Aboluyali
  82,12,Bamanya koosi kamukholanga
  82,13,"Toto\tAbakholi\tbamalayi\tbaliba mubwokholo"
  82,14,Ne toto Abakholi betsimbi baliba mumulilo
  82,15,Balinjilamwo inyanga yomurungo
  82,16,Ne shibalinyalilwa okhurulamwo tawe
  82,17,Ne ni shina shilakhumanyia inyanga yomurungo eyo
  82,18,Khandi ni shina shilakhumanyia inyanga yomurungo eyo
  82,19,"Inyanga yo Omundu alikhaywa okhokhoonya owundi shiosi shiosi, ne inyanga eyo obunyali bwoosi buliba bwa Nyasaye yenyene"
  83,1,Bali khushibi Abakalakala beshipimo
  83,2,"Balia abeene nibeepimila\tkhubandu benyanga betsusilibwe"
  83,3,Nabo nibapimila Abandu khushipimo nahomba khuratili bakatia
  83,4,"Koo!\tShibaparangakhwo\tmbu bakhayabululwe mubafu"
  83,5,Olwe inyanga ikhongo
  83,6,Inyanga yabandu baliema imbeli wa Omulesi webilonje biosi
  83,7,Shikali kario tawe! (Shinga olwa mukholanga) toto bwene ebikhole bia aboononi bili mushitabu shilangwa mbu Sijjin
  83,8,Ne nishina shikhumanyia sijjiin ino
  83,9,Ni eshitabu shiahandikwamwo (ebikhole bia abonooni)
  83,10,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanya eyo shiliba khubakhayi
  83,11,Balia bakhayanga (okhusuubila) inyanga yeyindukho
  83,12,Ne shakhayanga okhusuubila inyanga eyo okhuyiniakhwo ulia wabura eshichelo omukholi wetsimbi
  83,13,"Nasoomelwa ebimanyisio biefu naboola mbu: “etso ni tsingano etsia bakhale !”"
  83,14,Shikali kario tawe! habula emioyo chiabu chakhupa tsindebelende okhurulana khu kalia kabakholanga
  83,15,Shikali kario tawe! Toto bwene abo inyaga eyo balikalilwa okhunyoola tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi
  83,16,ne mana bakhenjile mumulilo
  83,17,"Mana baboolelwe mbu : “kano niko kamwakhayanga.”"
  83,18,Shikali kario tawe! (Shinga lwa mukholanga)! toto bwene ebikhole bia abamalayi bili mushitabu shilangwa mbu I’liyyin
  83,19,Nishina shikhumanyia I’liyyin ino
  83,20,Ni eshitabu shiahandikwamwo (ebikhole bia abonooni)
  83,21,Bakhashilole biala abalobole
  83,22,Toto bwene abakholi abamalayi baliba mubwokholo
  83,23,Balikhala khubifumbi bioluyali ni bahenga
  83,24,Olibamanyila khukhumesamesa khwo obweni bwabu ukhurulana khu obwokholo
  83,25,balinywesibwa ibinywebwa abilayi biafunikhwa
  83,26,Mukhumalikha khwabio (ebinywebwa ebo) biwunya obulayi shinga imisk. Ne khulwa okhunyoola kano bashilane balia abenya okhushilana
  83,27,Ne shiasasibwamwo nende (amaatsi ka) Tasniim
  83,28,(Tasniim eyo) ni Isebele yabalobole balinywamwo
  83,29,Toto bwene Abakholi betsimbi batsekhanga abasuubili
  83,30,Nibaburanga ewabali babakhondiolanga nibechesania
  83,31,Ne ni bakalukha mubandu babu bakalukha nibasangaalile
  83,32,"Ne nibabalola baboola mbu: “toto bano nibo bakora.”"
  83,33,Nabo abo shibarumwa okhuba abalindi babu tawe
  83,34,Olwa lelo Abasuubila nibo bastsekha Abakhayi
  83,35,Nibekhaale khubifumbi nibahenga
  83,36,"Ne\tkho!\tAbakhayi\tbarunjilwe khukabakholanga"
  84,1,Olwelikulu liliarukha
  84,2,"Ne olwa liliwulila Nyasaye walio, shingala lialachilwa okhumuwulila"
  84,3,Olwe liloba lilikwalaasibwa
  84,4,Mana liarusia biosi bilimwo liaba likhaya
  84,5,"Ne olwa liliwulila Nyasaye walio, shingala lialachilwa okhumuwulila"
  84,6,"Ewe Omundu! Toto ewe oleeminjia eshinani shishio okhulolana nende Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, mana Olimunyoola"
  84,7,Ne ulia owulihebwa eshitabu shishie no mukhono kukwe omulunji
  84,8,Kho oyo okhubalwa khukhwe khuliba okhwangu
  84,9,Ne alikalushila Abandu bebe nali nomwikhoyo
  84,10,Ne ulia ulihelesibwa eshitabu shishie namukongo wuwe
  84,11,Kho oyo alisaba okhulala
  84,12,Ne ilinjila mumulilo
  84,13,Toto ye yali mubandu be nali nomwikhoyo
  84,14,Toto ye yaparanga mbu shalikalukha khandi tawe
  84,15,"Kali mbu, toto bwene Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi yamulolanga"
  84,16,Ne nditsuba khubwakhanyu bweliuba nilitsia okhukwa
  84,17,Nende khushilo nende shia shibuusinjia
  84,18,Nende khu Omwesi shingala kukhongoyanga
  84,19,Toto bwene mwitsa okhunina eshisia khu khushisia
  84,20,Bali barie abalasuubilanga
  84,21,Ne nibasoomelwa Ikurani shibasujudanga tawe
  84,22,Halali balia abakhaya bayingananga butswa
  84,23,Ne Nyasaye amanyile kabenya okhukhola
  84,24,Kho basuubisie eshinyasio eshilulu
  84,25,"Halali balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, abo baliba nende umurungo kulawa tawe"
  85,1,Nditsuba khu likulu lie tsing’ining’ini
  85,2,Nende khuinyanga yalakwa
  85,3,Nende khumuloli nende shikholelwa obuloli
  85,4,Basishibwa Abandu bethingoba
  85,5,Omulilo kwe tsikhwi tsinyinji
  85,6,Olwabali nibekhale awo(khumulilo)
  85,7,Nabo nibo abaloli khu kalia kabakholelanga Abasuubili
  85,8,Nabo shibalolakhwo khubo obubii bwosi bwosi tawe habula okhusuubila khwabu khu Nyasaye Owamani Owa oluyali
  85,9,Uli nende obwami bwo mwikulu nende khushialo ne Nyasaye nomuloli wabuli eshindu
  85,10,"Toto balia bakhoba Abasuubili Abasatsa nende Abasuubili Abakhasi mana nibalekanila , balinyoola ishinyasio shiomulilo ne balinyoola eshinyasio eshiokhusambwa"
  85,11,"Toto bwene balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi balinyoola emikunda chiburangamwo imialo, ne okho nikho okhubura okhukhongo"
  85,12,Toto bwene eshinyasio shia Nyasaye wuwo neshilulu
  85,13,"Toto ye aranjilisinjia\tkhandi niye ukalusinjia"
  85,14,naye niwobulesheli owobuyanzi muno
  85,15,Oweshifumbi shioluyali
  85,16,uwukholanga muno akayenya
  85,17,Koo! Wawulilakhwo olukano lwabalwani be liyie
  85,18,Aba Firauni nende Thsamudi
  85,19,halali abakhayi bali mukhuyingasia butswa
  85,20,Ne Nyasaye yababotokhana munyuma mwabu
  85,21,Halali ino ni Ikurani yoluyali
  85,22,Ili khulupao lwalindwa
  86,1,Nditsuba khulikulu nende shokhwitsa eshilo
  86,2,Ne nishina eshikhumanyia mbu nishina esho shitsanga eshilo
  86,3,Ing’ining’ini yili nende obulafu obunji
  86,4,Buli shiamundu ali nende umuhenganga
  86,5,Ne Omundu ahenge yalongwa okhurulana nende shina
  86,6,"Yalongwa\tokhurulana\tkhu\tmatsi karulanga nikamitsikha"
  86,7,Karulanga hakarikari mulukongofuma nende omukongo
  86,8,Toto bwene Nyasaye ali nende obunyali bwokhumukalusia
  86,9,Inyanga ya kalia kefisa kalirebwa habulafu
  86,10,Abwene aho shaliba nende amani nohomba Omuhabini tawe
  86,11,"Nditsuba\tkhulikilu\tlili\tnende amakalushilo"
  86,12,Nende liloba liarukhanga
  86,13,"Toto\tbwene\tlino\tnilikhuwa lwokhwawukhasia"
  86,14,Nalio shilili emibayo tawe
  86,15,Toto bwene abo batutanga bututa
  86,16,Na siesi ndamanya obututi bwabu po
  86,17,Mana bahelesie ebise abakhayi- kaala kaala
  87,1,Witsoomie elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Owoluyali
  87,2,Owaloonga mana naleng’aasia
  87,3,ulia wabalilila mana nalunjisia
  87,4,ulia Owamesia olwayilo
  87,5,Mana nalukhola oluumila olumali
  87,6,Khulakhusomesia mana sholibilila tawe
  87,7,"halali Nyasaye nachama, toto ye amanyile kali habulafu nende kefisile"
  87,8,Ne khutsia okhuwanguyilisia kabe amangu
  87,9,"Mana itsulisia, nikali mbu okhwitsulisia khukhoonya"
  87,10,Yetsa okhwitsulila ulia uria
  87,11,Ne yetsa okhwira ehale nayo omukori
  87,12,Ulia ulinjila mumulilo omukhongo
  87,13,"Mana\tshalifwamwo\tnohomba shalihonokokhamwo tawe"
  87,14,Toto yamala okhubura ulia wetswenula
  87,15,Mana niyetsulila elira lia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mana nalaama
  87,16,Halali enywe mwayanza muno obulamu bwo khushialo
  87,17,Ne obulamu bwo mwikulu nobulayi ne nibwakhatsotso. (obulaliwa tawe)
  87,18,Toto kano kali mubitabo bie imbeli
  87,19,Ebitabu bia Ibrahim nende Musa
  88,1,Koo! Kakhwitsilakhwo amacheni kamasila kalifundesia Abandu
  88,2,obweni inyanga eyo bulitutuya
  88,3,Bukholele emilimo buchoonyele
  88,4,bulinjila mumulilo kwakhanga
  88,5,"Bulinywesibwa\tamatsi\tkeyisebele karabachilanga"
  88,6,shibalinyolamwo eshiakhulia tawe halali shiamawa
  88,7,Si shikhomesia nohomba sishimala inzala tawe
  88,8,Inyanga eyo obweni bundi buliba nibunula
  88,9,Buliba obulekhule khukhukhalabana khwabwo
  88,10,baliba mumukunda chioluyali
  88,11,Shibaliwulilamwo akeshifwabi tawe
  88,12,Mukariomoilimwo isebeleikhulukusinjia
  88,13,Ebifumbi bilimwo bie hekulu
  88,14,Nende tsigilasi tsiarebwa khulala
