  89,16,"Ne namutema mana amuleemie omukabo kwe aboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje yasukuna!”"
  89,17,Shikali kario tawe! Halali enywe shimuhenganga Abafwilwa neshisa tawe
  89,18,Nohomba shimutinyisaninjia okhulisia Abamanani tawe
  89,19,Ne mulitsanga emiandu chiabafwilwa okhulia khwatoto
  89,20,Ne mwayanza emiandu obuyanzi obuunji muno
  89,21,Shikali kario tawe! olwe eshialo shilifunakwa ebitonye ebitonye
  89,22,Ne aliitsa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi nende Abamalaika olunyali olunyali
  89,23,"Ne omulilo kwa Jahannamu kulireerwa inyanga eyo, omundu inyanga eyo alitsulila , halali okhwitsulila okho shikhulimukhoonya shiosi shiosi tawe"
  89,24,"Aliboola mbu: “manyanga ndakharanjisiliyie ebikhole ebilayi mubulamu bwanje!”"
  89,25,Mana inyanga eyo abulaho yesi yesi ulihelesia eshinyasio shinga eshinyasio shisie
